Package: kfre
Type: Package
Title: KFRE Risk Prediction Tools (R)
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
    c(person(given = "Leonid",
             family = "Shpaner",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "lshpaner@ucla.edu"))
Description: Implements the Kidney Failure Risk Equation (KFRE; Tangri et al.)
    to compute 2- and 5-year kidney failure risk (4-, 6-, and 8-variable
    models), append risk columns to data frames, classify CKD stages and ESRD
    outcomes, and evaluate and plot model performance.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    R (>= 3.6)
Imports:
    grDevices,
    ggplot2,
    R6
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0), knitr, rmarkdown, readxl, svglite, devtools, rprojroot
Config/testthat/edition: 3
